Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬不要握住任何人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這會給對方帶來不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也包括你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,握住彼此的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在異世界戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想將自己的願望傳達給神明的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在不斷勝出的 Hand  Shakers 最終
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,將抵達神的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,願望是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,願望是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,與神的對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,願望的實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,10年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跨越諸多戰鬥   克服無數試煉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,領受啟示之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欲謁見吾   挑戰吾之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,汝稱之為 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣   珠珠   像不像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,像不像那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說   文文   這音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喔   無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還只是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卻還挺有動感氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,滿帶感的嘛   這音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小華  小華
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喔   是那個叫「Y' s」的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早的   吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,超厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡厲害了   麻煩解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,別問了   聽就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瀨馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能停止那刺耳的音樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來以為需要音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,來沖散這如此倦怠的午後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,又碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要多注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不過   還好似乎是不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fs70}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有音樂科的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz11.88\pos(878.933,306.333)}新消息  發信人：爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,錯字還是一如既往的多
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.02,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDBF6C4&\4c&HDBF6C4&\fs55\b0\frz11.83\pos(854.8,315)}我廳你媽說了   你要去北飛鳥學園
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.38,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDBF6C4&\4c&HF4F4F4&\fs55\b0\frz11.83\pos(719.2,493.4)}爸爸我絕隊反對
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.13,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDBF6C4&\4c&HDBF6C4&\fs55\b0\frz11.83\pos(779.2,639.4)}和你說過憋去那裡
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDBF6C4&\4c&HDBF6C4&\fs55\b0\frz11.83\pos(735.2,811.4)}我生氣了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDBF6C4&\4c&HDBF6C4&\fs55\b0\frz11.83\pos(793.2,965.4)}家庭會議！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得那孩子很可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是初中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,挺帥的  來照一張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不契合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,請問是父親的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫北條勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你有聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有   非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,14歲   大概
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的初中生   身高還真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就是高中生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽說過北飛鳥學園嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那個   我想去的正是那所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡有一位名為芥川的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好和那個人見一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川？ 那個人是從事音樂相關的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼   我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是我爸爸的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,遙為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為輕音部的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是有輕音部的聚會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天幸也不是說想參加北飛鳥學園的參觀日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說   我也想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,卻偶然遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,剛好我一個人去心裡沒底   真高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只是今天幸也會去真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你只對音樂科有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可今天是普通科和機械科而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這個昨天妳倒是早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是記錯日期了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,唉   真不契合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就像曲和曲之間連接不契合的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說DJ的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我多少能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不契合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好了   別在意別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也的這種地方從小學開始一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,往積極的方向想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,至少沒錯過音樂科的日子   沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,遙也是從小時候開始都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都這麼積極向上   真令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在學校也和大家相處得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還很開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我   內心是非常纖細的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是說   說點什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是   果然還是很羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我放送的視頻也不怎麼順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   並沒有其他意思   是指音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,點擊率都沒什麼增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,原來沒在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我果真沒有才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在網路上都依然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也和我是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,關於提高播放量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,計劃是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不是有些人搞不懂PV是怎麼拍攝的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,比如在懸崖上或在大樓上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘗試一下那種方法如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,話題性…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有點難度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼頭緒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛   怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…那裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然知道的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我會幫忙的   好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎   好嗎   好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就選在今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是就是所謂的約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟別人也在約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又是在晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也要是化身成一匹狼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會積極考慮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我會積極考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這裡開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是   畢竟不是約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但積極思考   好歹是兩人一起的演奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡人這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不過不是的   妳大概會很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因為回來的時候一定會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想請妳握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,妳有聽到什麼聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要戴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只是加以改造而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也是    遙是聽不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看那後面的店員   完全是我喜歡的型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在這時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是這裡沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊   上面顯示的是直播
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這是那個世界沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,握手就能進去的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,從那直播的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太強了   竟然能辦到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,太強了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他把器材也帶進去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那個世界應該帶不了那麼大的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊   這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果打敗他   可以奪走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,離我們這裡挺近的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真帶感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有夠High
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,時隔十年再次出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,非常規的 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也   怎麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要報上名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我討厭這樣的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞的模樣真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是「Connect」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小華  為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼   這究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我再怎麼積極思考也無法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了   開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太性急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這就結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太厲害了   那傢伙真是太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然擋住你的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼好開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在山上   遇到人通常都會打聲招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是「理格爾 · 派爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正孝也快點   這是禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,別叫我的真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,「貝堤爾烏斯 · 派爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那你們是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們並沒有那種名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊是無視   一邊是沒名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊那個女孩的「寧錄」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1135.333,981.333)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,「寧錄」？  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(793.333,981.333)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是武器啊   像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是 Hand Shakers 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個世界戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,賭上願望的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那便是所謂的 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,即使不是自己期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓我們等到何時啊   真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,正孝   打敗他們   把那能力奪過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒那傢伙   讓這事早點結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我想和小華普通的手牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,當全部結束後   妳會忘掉這一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只有現在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跨越諸多戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,克服無數試煉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,領受啟示之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欲謁見吾   挑戰吾之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,據說暫時沒有我們的戲份
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,翠少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就讓在下「斯蒂安 · 瀨馬」來填補空缺的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是這影像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,乍看之下可能只是下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,實際是有下集預告的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,無預告時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有預告時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瀨馬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓您感到開心真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,次回W' z「ShE  SaW  Soul」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待

